fr fr CURSED ML/AI Implementation Validation
fr fr Final validation that all modules are accessible

yeet "mathz"
yeet "vibez"

fr fr Validate core mathematical operations
sus math_test drip = add_two(10, 5)
vibez.spill("✅ mathz module loaded: 10 + 5 = ", math_test)

fr fr Validate vibez module
vibez.spill("✅ vibez module loaded: I/O operations working")

